Overall Sales and Profit Summary

SELECT
    SUM(sales_amount) AS total_sales,
    SUM(profit) AS total_profit
FROM sales;

-This query calculates the overall sales and total profit from the sales dataset.
-Gives a high-level business overview
-Used for KPI cards in Power BI
-Helps stakeholders quickly understand overall performance
-Sales and profit columns contain valid numeric values
-No grouping is required since this is a summary-level analysis

Profit margin 
SELECT
  SUM(profit) / NULLIF(SUM(sales), 0) AS profit_margin
FROM sales;
